Summary
Exposes hand joint data on XrInputSources for use during a WebXr session. This allows developers to have more fine grained interactions during WebXr sessions.
Blink component Blink&gt;WebXR&lt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/list?q=component:Blink%3EWebXR"&gt;https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/list?q=component:Blink%3EWebXR&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
